Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:11.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess's concert held in Grana was really exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:16.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it wasn't only at the venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:22.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who watched the live telecast enjoyed themselves too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:26.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Thank you for your time tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:35.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's smiles and rising applause greeted the end of the concert,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:43.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and, together with the dawn, the citizens of Galette started heading back to Galette.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:49.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The citizens of Biscotti also returned to the land of Biscotti. Each went their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:39.97,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(450,0)\pos(139,353)}  「The Four Conditions」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:44.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a grand welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:46.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:52.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero, Yuki, I would like to excuse myself and then head to the institute.{This line shows up long after she starts talking}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:53.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:56.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, do say hello to everyone on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:11.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:14.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:18.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How does the issue of the deportation ceremony look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:25.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the equation for the ritual was resolved this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:29.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're ready, we can start the deportation at any time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:38.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The conditions for deportation to return the summoned hero to his own world are stated as follows:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:43.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One, the person who summoned him needs to perform the deportation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:50.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Two, the period between the summoning and the deportation needs to be within sixteen days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:59.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Three, the summoned hero is not allowed to take anything he received or achieved from Flonyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:13.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Four, once the hero is deported, he will never be able to return to Flonyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:17.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone else know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:19.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't told anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:24.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The final date of deportation is... three days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:28.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:41.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:46.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've managed to come up with a way for you to return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:55.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the plan, you'll be able to return home the morning of three days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:59.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! Well, that's what I want to say, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is there a catch to it?{are there any drawbacks?}{drawbacks? setbacks? literally, are there any catch?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A hero who has been summoned before
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:09.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will never be able to come back to Flonyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:20.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And there is also the condition that you're not \Nallowed to take anything you received in Flonyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:27.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This refers not only to material things but also includes knowledge and experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:34.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the memories of your time in Flonyard will be erased when you're deported.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:35.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:40.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is why... you've looked pale since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:45.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just too worthless to be chief of the research institute.{She's the one suffering the most. -sm} {AL: crappy = disappointing; worthless; pusillanimous; feckless}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:50.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have assumed things to be too simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could do it, no matter how difficult it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:57.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so sure something this depressing wouldn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:01.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't your fault, Rico.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:05.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Positive thinking is one of your good points.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:11.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been getting along so well with the princess and everyone here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:15.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and you've always been hanging out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all getting along so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:20.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want this to end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:29.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,about Flonyard and everyone here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:33.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I want you to stay here forever!{I think I'll feel like killing *a certain scientific someone* if this becomes the release screenshot... nvm the seemingly harsh tone :D -sm}{AL: i agree with sm... i'll kill him}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:42.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it'll be very tough for us not to meet again and for me to forget about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:46.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:51.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even if I return home, I won't forget about everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:55.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the feeling that I'll definitely be able to come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico, am I the first to know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:06.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, except for those in the research institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:09.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, could you do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:19.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to keep the facts that I won't be able to come back
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:24.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and that I'll lose my memories a secret from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:30.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel kind of lonely the minute I think about leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:34.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If everyone says goodbye as if we'll never meet again,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:37.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll feel that it'll definitely happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:38.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:44.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to go back home with the \Nfeeling that I can see everyone again someday.{Nice way of thinking, hopefully should work out. And are we looking at a possibility of S2 here? -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:52.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, you seem to be in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:56.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Everyone enjoyed the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I made up with Princess Leo again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:03.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I will be going for a \Nmorning walk with Sink tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:06.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That really is something to look forward to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:12.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, will Sir Hero be attending tomorrow's practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know? Why are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:20.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you have been very close with him all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:22.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's close to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?! And who would be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:29.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he'd go to Fugetsu at noon, \Nso he'll probably come by in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero will be coming over tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Around noon, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:39.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be paying this little one a visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:43.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and he'll also have a little sword practice with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:48.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to prepare a lot more for lunch then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:51.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you cool the fruits in the well too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:51.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:55.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done with the little things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:00.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go out tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To go to Sink's with the three fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:08.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized that I didn't properly settle things with him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:14.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's up to you. I'll visit Biscotti the following day myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Arumi, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Then I'll just stay over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:24.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, just don't give the people any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:30.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you've found a way to send Sink home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:37.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so you will be in charge of the deportation ceremony in the morning three days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:43.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably won't be able to come back right afterward, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:47.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink really is going back. I'll miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:54.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will miss him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:00.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:08.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, it's my turn next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bully me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, you've dropped something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:21.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:25.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You always seem to be carrying this around, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:31.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is the prize from the competition that you saw through the star reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:34.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a memento for getting second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:38.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It must be an important treasure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something sentimental and memorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:48.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:50.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:52.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man! {Another candidate for release screenshot :D -sm} {AL: boring image}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:54.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:58.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I came! Eclair, let's train together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:01.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sharpen my sword skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:05.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you don't mind getting hurt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for letting me come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:21.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the little fox doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:23.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He's getting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:29.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a land god myself, I'm taking good care of him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:30.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Land god?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:36.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the land god's children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki's a god?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:44.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. You can honor me if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents were killed by a demon long ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and with no place to go, I wandered around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then my lady decided to take me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:59.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I became a wanderer when a demon destroyed my country, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:02.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:06.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought countries could get destroyed here in Flonyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:10.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a story from roughly a hundred and fifty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:15.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For the last hundred years, the demon hasn't revealed itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there aren't any dangerous disputes. Only peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:22.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Yukikaze and I possess the power to seal demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:25.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've made Biscotti our stronghold during these past few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:30.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once in a while we visit other countries and seal demons there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that Lady d'Arquien is also a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:39.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, due to various circumstances, I had been able to live a rather long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:45.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice it'd be if you could continue to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:52.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could pass on my sword skills and sealing abilities, such as Flashing Fangs of the Divine Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:57.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, Flashing Fangs of the Divine Wolf \Nis something that only she can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow when you say that, it sounds very tempting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why don't I show it to you for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1650)}Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:13.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:18.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's really impossible to learn it all within one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul! And everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:27.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? You went somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to Fugetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:33.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Sink, Sink! We brought you some souvenirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a combination of Galette's famous delights.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:39.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do take it back to your homeworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister said that it's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:46.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I must find it! {This is why she's my favourite character. -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:58.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a way in which it won't end sadly for Sir Hero and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:07.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Prince Gaul is strong! Prince Gaul is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:09.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sink hasn't lost either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:13.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep everyone waiting. I brought the drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:15.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Vert,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:19.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for troubling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dah! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:27.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?! You did it again?! {The frame at 14:29.118 -- 20838, I vote for this to be the release pic please, :D -sm} {AL: i'd rather the next scene}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:33.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sowwie! {Does she say "gomen-nya-sai" the second time? -sm} {AL: okay......}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:40.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, the next time Vert stands behind you, you'd better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why don't you go take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:49.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll finish cleaning while you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:52.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:57.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, this time it would be a separate bath for men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:15:01.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way to the men's bath, and this way to the women's bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I won't go wrong this time!{So confident, but it's his luck lol. -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:05.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useful to learn after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:12.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I made a mistake! {Oh nice. Great timing. -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:20.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:23.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a mistake again?! I'm so dead! {AL: i kinda feel sad for him}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:27.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:29.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:29.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:33.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, the wrong sign was hung at the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:38.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the only ones who entered here were ladies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:42.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry! I'm the only one here!{Such a considerate person ^_^ -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:47.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! I'll fix it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:54.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,could you stay like that for a while?{Well, maybe this can make do for a release screenshot too... -sm} {AL: ==" you people have bad taste}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:56.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:02.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's okay now.{Well done, Sink, for hanging in there :D -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:10.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've put on a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to get in together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:15.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, okay... {Lucky him!! -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:19.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sink...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:20.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:24.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When will you return here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:27.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That depends on how long I would stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:29.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's only a couple of days, then I can come during Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's two weeks or longer, then it'd have to be summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'll be soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:39.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be great if your friends could come along next time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca and Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:47.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're your friends, the castle would welcome them with open arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:50.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:54.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sink...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:55.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:59.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still remember my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:07.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Millhiore Frianno Biscotti, Millhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:10.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Millhi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:11.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:24.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't call you that in front of \Nother people. They'll go after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:30.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not that I want you to call me otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:34.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be happy that you'll remember my name and never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:39.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Millhiore. I have a pet name, Millhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:50.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really feel it's easier to call you Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:52.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:53.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, hand!{Split this line and added ellipsis. -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:54.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:55.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, the other hand! {your other hand or the other hand? how do you talk to your dogs? lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:56.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!{Added. -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:18:00.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good girl! Princess, well done! Princess, you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:06.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a simple gesture, but I wonder why I feel so happy! {I think it's because of your inherent doglike instincts, Princess. -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:37.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I heard that you are going back home. It's tomorrow already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:46.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to thank you and practice with you after Gaul for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when I visit next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is comfortable to be petted by Millhi. {So, she's a lion-like character. That explains why she's enjoying it so much. And she and the Princess are like cat and dog, and friends at that. -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:57.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo's touch is unique too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:00.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness is this kind of character?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:06.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it's about age, Princess Leo is slightly older,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:06.49,Dialogue Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Millhi... I want more... {I *think* that Sankaku will (or might've already) interpreted this as "shoujo ai" etc etc, but it's not like that lol... -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:09.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but fundamentally, our princess is the older sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:07.91,Dialogue Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:14.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,while Princess Leo is the younger sister, when they interact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:26.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm allowed in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:28.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously. Why would I bring you if you weren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:30.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:35.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone, Hero Sink has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:45.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in Frianno Castle, today, as per stated in the emergency notice, {i just realized her name is the same as this castle... what did we put her name as previously? can we change it to Frianno? lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:52.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Sink, who has helped save our country from danger, will return to his homeworld tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:59.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Sink's exploits have added much color to the neighbor wars between Biscotti and Galette.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:03.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure that everyone knows about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:11.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he'll be going back to his homeworld, he's promised to come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:24.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, let's invite the main star of today's "Thank you Sir Hero" gathering to say a word or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, please come forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:29.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:57.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where I come from, I'm just a normal student.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:21:00.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the princess summoned me to Flonyard as a hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:06.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then I fought with Prince Gaul and Princess Leo and participated in wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:10.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that I exterminated a demon with the princess, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:13.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from war activities, Leader of the Knights, Lady d'Arquien,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Imperial Guard, Panettone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:21.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Elmar, Captain Rizel, and everyone on the maid's team,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:24.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Emilio, and the Knights army...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have all been so nice to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! And the aunt from the canteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:34.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She always let Rico and me dine at the cafeteria. Thank you! {Nice of him, not forgetting to credit anyone :) -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:35.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:41.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had incredible experiences here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:45.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I return to my homeworld, I'll never forget my experience here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:49.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely come visit again soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:52.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Biscotti and Flonyard face a pinch,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:57.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the hero, Sink, will appear no matter when!{A hint of Season 2? I want one :3 -sm}
